"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-10-08-Cardboard-beds-of-Paris-Olympic-Village-shipped-away-for-second-life-1xwB2UpZBUQ-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  A cardboard bed in the Olympic Village in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2561411796416914e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 269, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999960102741, \"rank\": 3.989831227547934e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9952525543864161, \"rank\": 0.004479735615867456, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  The 16,000 cardboard beds have been taken out of the Olympic Village for the 2024 Summer Games in Paris for second life.\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2561411796416914e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999960102741, \"rank\": 3.989831227547934e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tony Estanguet, President of the Games, said that the move is part of the double vision of Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999488864, \"rank\": 5.110766304665076e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From the beginning, Paris 2024 had a double vision,\\\" Estanguet told reporters.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To have a spectacular Games but also a responsible Games and all our partners were involved in those two ambitions.\\\"\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Speaking about the legacy and sustainability of the games\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6the responsibility of the Games, we tried to imagine how much we can guarantee and provide a second life for all the equipment used for Paris 2024,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999488864, \"rank\": 5.110766304665076e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cardboard beds were first introduced to the Olympic Games in Tokyo in 2021.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8753937927835338, \"rank\": 0.14234146173481912, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japanese mattress brand Airweave was the official bedding supporter of them and they brought these cardboard beds to Paris for the 2024 Olympics and Paralympics.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9190762432193242, \"rank\": 0.08589581639089319, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1128, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999960102741, \"rank\": 3.989831227547934e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We designed these cardboard beds so that they can support up to three or four people jumping, because after winning a medal, people are very happy,\\\" said Motokuni Takaoka, founder and president of Airweave.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1338, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takaoka_Castle\", \"score\": 0.7053302165119121, \"rank\": 0.41772916237489066, \"text\": \"Takaoka\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q23413\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takaoka_Castle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Takaoka_Castle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, we will donate to a diverse (group) of organization's in France,\\\" said Chie Fujii, Logistics Manager of Airweave Paris 2024 Project.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9952525543864161, \"rank\": 0.004479735615867456, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And yes, the mattress is totally washable.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No bed bugs!\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Which will make it easy to facilitate the second life.\\\"\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": []}]}"